The data include fasta files of alignments of the following genes:

Control1 - 3 pluripotency markers:
POU5F1,	SOX2, 	NANOG

Test1 - 11 IGF signalling genes:
IGF1,	IGF2,	IGF1R,	IGF2R,	IGFBP2,	IGFBP4,	IGFBP5,	PAPPA,	PAPPA2,	STC1,	STC2

Test2 - 10 Upregulated genes from Fu et al.:
HDHD2,	HADH,	HK2,	PSMA7,	COX17,	COX5A,	ABAT,	DAP,	CAPZB,	PMPCA

Control2- 20 Randomly selected genes from OrthoMaM database:
ACTR1A,	DDIT4,	DOOST,	EHF,	EVPL,	GAS7,	MAP1B,	MRPL27,	MYO1A,	NPAS4,	PAFAH1B3,
PAQR3,	PHF24,	POLR1C,	QRICH1,	TGFB3,	TGM1,	USH1C,	ZC3HC1,	ZCCHC17
